data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled on a spacious corner quarter-acre lot. This beautifully maintained property boasts 1506 sqft of living space and features a FENCED yard for added privacy. Inside, you'll find modern upgrades including dark wood floors that add warmth and character throughout. This house is only 5 years old, so enjoy the added bonus of a newer roof, water heater and HVAC. This home is on county taxes which means its SAVING YOU MONEY! Speaking of money savers!! SOLAR PANELS are paid off, keeping monthly electricity costs lower! Pack up and move in! This house is ready to be your HOME!
